Subject: Navigating Polyamory: Keeping your Cups Full
Description: Join us for a presentation and Q&A about one million different ways to practice poly. Come learn how to better communicate and work through hiccups, such as scheduling conflicts, new partners, sexual safety, and mental/emotional health.  Speakers include:Andrew M. "Fish" Popowich, Becky Hill, Cyndi Chadwick - Track: Life  - Duration: 1 hour
